Sofia Vergara, 50, showed off her hourglass figure as she posed for a mirror selfie on Instagram before partying the night away with her celeb pals. The America's Got Talent judge and Modern Family actress stunned in the black mini dress, featuring a long ribbon trailing over her legs at the front, covering her modesty and halting a near wardrobe malfunction. The Hollywood paired the leg-flashing dress with black tights, heels and a large silver bangle while styling her brunette tresses in a wavy look. Sofia also went for a smokey-eyed look, paired with a dark lip, showing off her flawless appearance. She partied the night away with the likes of Heidi Klum, Jessica Alba, Priyanka Chopra and Sharon Stone as they met up for their mutual friend, makeup entrepreneur Anastasia Soare's, anniversary party.